articles.author: Stuart Lau
articles.title: NATO has air defense systems ready for Ukraine, Stoltenberg says - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: Announcements are expected “in the near future,” the NATO Secretary General said after Zelenskyy met with defense ministers.
articles.content: "NATO defense ministers have agreed to step up and provide further military support, including more air defense. NATO has mapped out existing capabilities across the lines and there are systems that … [+644 chars]
